{"tid":604910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翻新樂華冬菇亭 領展逼走34年街坊飯堂","createTime":"2018-03-25T07:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T10:10:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6c4836f45947ce8c6d991387847b7db0b82e69","tid":604910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:31:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180325/20342175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342175&d=oaWwkkh%2B5ILexk9J9XZkAxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=116ffbc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342175&h=dbde2f2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180325/20342175</a><br />\n<br />\n翻新樂華冬菇亭<br />\n領展逼走34年街坊飯堂<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】在牛頭角樂華南邨冬菇亭經營34年的泰興粉麵燒臘，今午結束營業。老闆曾先生透露，領展決定翻新冬菇亭，並指明要做扒房或東南亞食肆，供應西式早餐、小炒、中式點心的泰興，被領展嫌棄「冇特色」，惟有結業離場。他不滿領展月初才通知不續約，「炒人都要一個月通知啦」，現希望另覓舖位重新開業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25la5p6.jpg&h=ee42bde9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂華南邨最後一個冬菇亭食肆泰興粉麵燒臘今日結業。黃耀興攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n店主稱月初始獲通知<br />\n<br />\n樂華南邨有3個冬菇亭，正被領展逐一改建，一個已改為「新冬菇亭」營運茶餐廳，另一個清空準備發展，只剩下泰興「原貌」經營。泰興24小時營業，除魚蛋粉麵、小炒及燒味等茶餐廳食品，更供應中式點心。從舅父手上接掌泰興經營3年的曾先生稱顧及基層食客，即使成本上升，每年僅加價1元，「唔係吓吓都講賺錢」。<br />\n<br />\n曾先生透露，過去兩年租約已縮至半年一簽，每次也會加租幾個百分點，惟2月底滿約前卻未有傾續約，再三追問下，本月5日才獲通知冬菇亭要翻新，不再續約，要求他月底遷出，「佢哋話要做扒房或東南亞嘢食，（領展）惡到要限埋你做乜生意」，他無奈決定結業。<br />\n<br />\n街坊飯堂結業，老顧客大感可惜。光顧30年的葉女士差不多每日也會與街坊到泰興食早餐，同枱三人有人食點心，有人食三文治，「呢啲咪大牌檔特色」。泰興結業她大感可惜，「我由個孫手抱食到中學畢業，好有感情」。<br />\n<br />\n熟客孔太指，泰興飲茶經濟實惠，「酒樓茶錢8蚊位再加一，呢度3蚊冇加一」，無奈之後只能光顧酒樓「飲貴茶」。20多歲的賴小姐為樂華居民，在泰興「由細食到大」，昨特別帶住港島區友人高小姐來飲茶，「佢唔知咩係冬菇亭」。賴指，外國朋友來港也會帶他光顧冬菇亭，若日後經營扒房或東南亞餐廳，「改裝到咁就冇晒特色」。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員何啟明及榮譽會長陳婉嫻昨到泰興了解。何指特首林鄭月娥上任時揚言要解決包括領展的「三座大山」，惟領展趕絕小商戶不停發生，促政府插手事件，例如審視地契有否條款可保障基層。<br />\n<br />\n■記者嚴敏慧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25la5p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25la5p7.jpg&h=22e8bd77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴小姐（左）特意帶住港島的高小姐到泰興飲茶。"},{"pid":"5d1b47fdd9717052edd0a5d5f954f8962565f591","tid":604910,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持823 上市丫拿<br />\n<br />\n焦土公屋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96830df75765e63081398e42f2c48b50f000893","tid":604910,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:20:22.000Z","msg":"領匯冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b5be2c5e5ab7e2275dc704efa31651bd86fbe2","tid":604910,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.people.com.cn/mediafile/200501/02/F2005010215215400000.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2Fmediafile%2F200501%2F02%2FF2005010215215400000.JPG&h=711fddd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.techpowerup.org/110207/20080831b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.techpowerup.org%2F110207%2F20080831b.jpg&h=d9abaf58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\t<img src=\"http://img.techpowerup.org/110207/2604769434481454943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.techpowerup.org%2F110207%2F2604769434481454943.jpg&h=21e5929a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5ce76cf1fefa1b5a80bd11ee90ddeb5890cfbd78","tid":604910,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1b47fdd9717052edd0a5d5f954f8962565f591","tid":604910,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:01:38.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持823 上市丫拿<br />\n<br />\n焦土公屋狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"社會要進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c3fe882a75235bbede30508c5c91a9df947e95","tid":604910,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"經營扒房或東南亞餐廳<br />\n<br />\n果個位搞呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cab9c6eb8263fc0af863d20a8a59d15e0fdbd37","tid":604910,"uid":66402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"領展 你值得擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b02bda9b0a192c37eee49581279264fe04185bc","tid":604910,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:01:40.000Z","msg":"屌 呢個位多老鼠到痴線<br />\n同老鼠一齊開餐的街坊食堂"},{"pid":"52d22696e2f10d847aaec4c9022a6fea017872ce","tid":604910,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁點姐 唔好諗著上報會有人可憐先得架"}]}